This view only exists due to the fact that the huge data amounts from BSEG and BKPF G0 are only loaded since Finscal Year 2021.   For reporting of Accounting Document Customer Cleared Items, the ones that have been cleared since 2021 are of interest (= filter on AUGDT from source REDLake). But: Some of these recently cleared items have been posted way earlier, in Fiscal Years < 2021.   This view covers these cases and closes the data gap with data from BSAD G0 for Fiscal Years < 2021. For Fiscal Years >= 2021, BSEG and BKPF provide necessary information instead.
